  99:funsape/peripheral/../util/systemStatus.hpp ****     //! \brief      System Clock prescaler enumeration.
 100:funsape/peripheral/../util/systemStatus.hpp ****     //! \details    Clock prescaler options associated with MCU System.
 101:funsape/peripheral/../util/systemStatus.hpp ****     //! \warning    The value associate with the symbolic names may change
 102:funsape/peripheral/../util/systemStatus.hpp ****     //!                 between builds and might not reflect the register/bits
 103:funsape/peripheral/../util/systemStatus.hpp ****     //!                 real values. In order to ensure compatibility between
 104:funsape/peripheral/../util/systemStatus.hpp ****     //!                 builds, always refer to the SYMBOLIC NAME, instead of
